flowchart LR
    COMP["🧩 Fully Composable\n────────────────\nAll tools are optional\nNo golden path enforced\nDevelopers choose everything\n\nExample: raw Kubernetes\n+ optional operator catalogue"]

    MID["⚖ Opinionated with Escape Hatches\n────────────────\nGolden paths are the default\nEscape hatches exist and are documented\nPlatform team owns the defaults\nTeams own exceptions\n\n← Most successful platforms land here"]

    OPIN["🏛 Fully Opinionated\n────────────────\nOne way to do everything\nNo deviation permitted\nPlatform team approves all changes\n\nExample: Heroku, internal PaaS"]

    COMP -->|"adds structure\nand defaults"| MID
    MID -->|"removes\nall flexibility"| OPIN

